svg.text: In general, most of the Kickstarter action happens in the UK. London with 6,131 projects in total (70 per 100,000 people)seems to be the most active city, but Manchester, for example, with a much smaller population has 546 projects per 100,000 people (604 projects in total).Countries colored in lighter grey do not have any Kickstarter project.
